          <title>Verstappen takes pole for Sunday's F1 Japanese Grand Prix ahead of Norris and Piastri</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SUZUKA, Japan (AP) — Max Verstappen of Red Bull will start from pole position in the Japanese Grand Prix after turning in the top time in qualifying on Saturday in his final attempt.]]></description>
