        <item>
          <title>Celtics set NBA record for 3-pointers in a season, passing Warriors' mark from 2022-23</title>
          <description><![CDATA[BOSTON (AP) — The Boston Celtics' season started with a record-tying 3-point night. It was a sign of things to come. The Celtics broke the NBA record for 3-pointers in a season Friday night in a victory over the Phoenix Suns. “We've got a really good team," star Jayson Tatum said.]]></description>
          <guid>https://majordigest.com/sports/2025/04/05/celtics-set-nba-record-for-3-pointers-in-a-season-passing-warriors-mark-from-2022-23/</guid>
