          <title>Brian Harman builds 4-shot lead at Texas Open</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SAN ANTONIO (AP) — Brian Harman found the range with his iron shots and converted eight birdie putts Friday, none outside 12 feet, for a 6-under 66 that gave him a four-shot lead over Keith Mitchell going into the weekend at the Valero Texas Open.]]></description>
